#. Tag: title
#: details-tags.docbook:11
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tags"
msgstr "Oznake"

#. Tag: para
#: details-tags.docbook:13
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Tags provide an additional way for you to group and categorize transactions. "
"They are often useful in <link linkend=\"details.search\">searching for "
"transactions</link> and for <link linkend=\"details.reports.avail\">creating "
"reports</link>."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: details-tags.docbook:20
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Tags List"
msgid "Tags View"
msgstr "Lista oznaka"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-tags.docbook:22
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>tags view transactions tab</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-tags.docbook:28
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "<phrase>Tag details</phrase>"
msgid "<phrase>tags view transactions tab</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Detalji o oznakama</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-tags.docbook:33
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The Tags screen provides detailed information about all the tags which "
#| "are applied to transactions. The Tags screen is split into two main "
#| "areas: a tags list and a detail area."
msgid ""
"The Tags View provides information about all the tags that have been added "
"to the data file. The display is split into two areas."
msgstr ""
"Prikaz oznaka daje detaljne informacije o svim oznakama koje su primijenjene "
"na transakcije. Prikaz oznaka je podijeljen u dvije glavne oblasti: lista "
"oznaka i oblast detalja."

#. Tag: title
#: details-tags.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tags List"
msgstr "Lista oznaka"

#. Tag: para
#: details-tags.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the left is a list of tags, with buttons for adding, renaming, or "
"deleting a tag."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: details-tags.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the right you can see more detailed information about the tag selected in "
"the list on the left, in one of the two tabs: Transactions and Details. The "
"<guilabel>Transactions</guilabel> tab displays all the transactions "
"associated with the tag. The <guilabel>Details</guilabel> tab includes a "
"user-selectable color, as well as Notes, which are not used elsewhere. Note "
"that if you change the color, which is used in the symbol displayed before "
"the tag name in any associated transactions, you need to click "
"<guibutton>Update</guibutton> at the lower right of the Details area for it "
"to be saved."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: details-tags.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding a Tag"
msgstr "Dodavanje oznake"

#. Tag: para
#: details-tags.docbook:56
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To add a tag, either click on the Add tag icon "
#| "<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"list-add.png"
#| "\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guiicon> or right-click on any "
#| "tag and choose <guimenuitem>New tag</guimenuitem>. This creates a new tag "
#| "called <quote>New tag</quote>. Right-click on this tag and select "
#| "<guimenuitem>Rename tag</guimenuitem> to enter the name of the new tag."
msgid ""
"As with most actions in &kmymoney;, there are multiple ways to create a new "
"tag. First, you can click the "
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"tag-new.svg\" "
"format=\"SVG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guiicon> new tag icon. "
"Second, you can right-click any tag and choose <guimenuitem>New tag...</"
"guimenuitem>. This creates a new tag called <quote>New tag.</quote> See the "
"next section for how to rename the tag. Finally, you can add a new tag "
"directly in the ledger or within a split transaction by typing the name of "
"the tag in the tag field. &kmymoney; will ask if you want to add this tag "
"and after selecting <quote>yes</quote> it will be added."
msgstr ""
"Za dodavanje oznake, možete kliknuti na ikonu dodaj oznaku  "
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"list-add.png\"/"
"></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guiicon>, ili kliknuti na bilo koju "
"oznaku desnim klikom i odabrati <guimenuitem>Nova oznaka</guimenuitem>. Ovo "
"kreira novu oznaku pod imenom <quote>Nova oznaka</quote>.  Odaberite ovu "
"oznaku desnim klikom i odaberite <guimenuitem>Promijeni ime oznake</"
"guimenuitem> da unesete ime nove oznake."

#. Tag: title
#: details-tags.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid "Renaming a Tag"
msgstr "Promjena imena oznake"

#. Tag: para
#: details-tags.docbook:70
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To rename a tag, either click on the tag name to select it and click on "
#| "the <guiicon>Rename tag</guiicon> (between the add and remove icons) or "
#| "right-click on the name and then select <guimenuitem>Rename tag</"
#| "guimenuitem>. The name then becomes editable. Changing the name will "
#| "affect the name in all the transactions in which it appears."
msgid ""
"To rename a tag, either click the tag name to select it and then click "
"<guiicon> <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"tag-edit.svg"
"\" format=\"SVG\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> </guiicon> Rename "
"Tag, or right-click the name and then select <guimenuitem>Rename tag</"
"guimenuitem>. The name then becomes editable. Changing the name will affect "
"the name in all the transactions in which it appears."
msgstr ""
"Da biste promijenili ime oznake, možete kliknuti na ime oznake da je "
"odabarete i kliknuti na <guiicon>Promijeni ime oznake</guiicon> (između "
"ikona za dodavanje i uklanjanje) ili odabrati ime desnim klikom i onda "
"odabrati <guimenuitem>Promijeni ime oznake</guimenuitem>. Nakon toga, ime se "
"može urediti. Promjena imena će se odraziti na sve transakcije u kojima se "
"oznaka pojavljuje."

#. Tag: title
#: details-tags.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid "Deleting a Tag"
msgstr "Brisanje oznake"

#. Tag: para
#: details-tags.docbook:81
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To remove a tag, either click on the Delete tag icon "
#| "<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"list-remove."
#| "png\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guiicon> or right-click the "
#| "name and select <guimenuitem>Delete tag</guimenuitem>. If the tag has any "
#| "transactions, you will be presented with a dialog that allows you to "
#| "reassign them to a different tag."
msgid ""
"To delete a tag, either select it and click <guiicon> <inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"tag-delete.svg\" format=\"SVG\"/></"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> </guiicon> delete tag or right-click the "
"tag name and select <guimenuitem>Delete tag</guimenuitem>. If the tag has "
"any transactions, you will be presented with a dialog that allows you to "
"reassign them to a different tag."
msgstr ""
"Da biste obrisali oznaku, možete kliknuti na ikonu obriši oznaku "
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"list-remove.png"
"\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guiicon> ili kliknuti desnom tipkom "
"miša na ime i odabrati <guimenuitem>Obriši oznaku</guimenuitem>. Ako oznaka "
"ima transakcija, biće vam ponuđen dijalog koji vam omogućava da ih "
"dodijelite nekoj drugoj oznaci."

#. Tag: para
#: details-tags.docbook:90
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "As Tags have just been introduced to &kappname; in version 4.7, none of "
#| "the methods for importing data are able to import tags. It is understood "
#| "that this is an important feature, and each import method is likely to "
#| "introduce it in an upcoming release."
msgid ""
"Tags were introduced to &kmymoney; in version 4.7, but not all of the "
"methods for importing data are able to import tags. It is understood that "
"this is an important feature, and it will eventually be added to all import "
"methods"
msgstr ""
"Kako su oznake tek uvedene u &kappname; u  verziji 4.7, nijedna od metoda za "
"uvoz podataka ne može uvoziti oznake. Razumljivo je da je ovo važna opcija, "
"tako da će vjerovatno svaka od metoda omogućiti uvoz oznaka u sljedećoj "
"verziji."

#. Tag: title
#: details-tags.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tagged transactions and Tag details"
msgstr "Označene transakcije i detalji oznaka"

#. Tag: para
#: details-tags.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To view the transactions or view and edit the information associated with a "
"particular tag, select the tag from the list and select the appropriate tab "
"on the right side of the dialog."
msgstr ""
"Za pregled transakcija ili pregled i uređivanje informacija vezanih za "
"pojedinačnu oznaku, odaberite oznaku iz liste i odaberite odgovarajuću "
"karticu na desnoj strani dijaloga."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-tags.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>tags view details tab</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-tags.docbook:113
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "<phrase>Tag details</phrase>"
msgid "<phrase>tags view details tab</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Detalji o oznakama</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: details-tags.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tagged transactions"
msgstr "Označene transakcije"

#. Tag: para
#: details-tags.docbook:119
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To see a list of the transactions associated with the selected tag, "
#| "select the <guilabel>Transactions</guilabel> tab. This list is similar to "
#| "the list of transactions for a Payee. You can double-click on a "
#| "transaction, and you will be taken to the ledger view of that transaction "
#| "for the account in which the transaction has been tagged."
msgid ""
"To see a list of the transactions associated with the selected tag, select "
"the <guilabel>Transactions</guilabel> tab. This list is similar to the list "
"of transactions for a Payee. You can double-click a transaction to edit it, "
"or you can right-click the transaction and select <guimenuitem>Go to "
"'Account name'</guimenuitem> to go to the Ledgers View of that transaction "
"in the account in which the transaction has been tagged."
msgstr ""
"Da biste vidjeli listu transakcija povezanih sa odabranom oznakom, odaberite "
"karticu <guilabel>Transakcije</guilabel>. Ova lista je slična listi "
"transakcija za primatelja uplate. Možete odabrati transakciju duplim klikom "
"lijeve tipke miša, i bit ćete odvedeni u prikaz knjige salda za račun u "
"kojem je transakcija označena."

#. Tag: title
#: details-tags.docbook:129
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "The tag details tab"
msgid "Tag details"
msgstr "Kartica detalja o oznakama"

#. Tag: para
#: details-tags.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To view and edit the information associated with a particular tag, select "
"the <guilabel>Details</guilabel> tab."
msgstr ""
"Za pregled i uređivanje informacija povezanih sa određenom oznakom, "
"odaberite karticu <guilabel>Detalji</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: details-tags.docbook:136
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You can select the color used to highlight transactions with which this "
#| "tag has been associated. If you click on the color bar, you will get a "
#| "color chooser dialog."
msgid ""
"You can select the color used to highlight transactions with which this tag "
"has been associated. If you click the color bar, you will get a color "
"chooser dialog."
msgstr ""
"Možete odabrati boju koja se koristi da se istaknu transakcije sa kojima je "
"ova oznaka povezana. Ako kliknete na traku boja, dobit ćete dijalog za "
"odabir boja."

#. Tag: para
#: details-tags.docbook:143
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking the <guilabel>Closed</guilabel> checkbox will not alter any "
"transactions already associated with the tag, but it will prevent assigning "
"the tag to any additional transactions."
msgstr ""
"Klikom na <guilabel>Zatvoreno</guilabel> komandni okvir neće promijeniti "
"nijednu transakciju povezanu sa oznakom, ali će spriječiti dodjelu oznake "
"dodatnim transakcijama."

#. Tag: para
#: details-tags.docbook:150
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To modify the notes associated with the tag, just edit the text in the box."
msgstr "Za modifikaciju bilješki povezanih sa oznakom, uredite tekst u kutiji."

#. Tag: para
#: details-tags.docbook:156
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "When you are done, don't forget to click the <guiicon>Update</guiicon> "
#| "button, although you will be prompted if you leave the dialog without "
#| "having done so."
msgid ""
"When you are done, don't forget to click <guiicon>Update</guiicon>, at the "
"lower right of the window, although you will be prompted if you try to leave "
"the dialog without having done so."
msgstr ""
"Kada završite, nemojte zaboraviti kliknuti na dugme <guiicon>Ažuriraj</"
"guiicon>, iako ćete biti pitani da li želite to uraditi ako napustite "
"dijalog prije nego što ste to uradili."

